{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d7080bf82b","title":"中央转发华东局关于组织人民法庭指示的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1bd57475aa","index":0,"year":1950,"month":8,"day":19,"articleId":"d7080bf82b"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"85a822ca8e","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d7080bf82b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共中央华东局1950年8月17日关于组织人民法庭的指示。指示规定：（一）应在特活动较为频繁及定子今冬进行土地改革之县份，首先建立人民法庭。（二）应在各县县委副书记、县农协主任、副县长或县公安局长等干部中，择一人兼任县人民法庭审判长，另以一得力的专职干部任副审判长。（三）确定担任人民法庭工作的干部及人员，应由各省（区）进行短期的专门训练。（四）应在干部较强、工作基础较好之县，先由县长或县委书记甚至专员，亲自审讯及办理一二个案件，作为示范，并吸取经验，以教育干部。"}],"contents":[{"id":"73043c1e7b","type":"title","text":"中央转发华东局关于组织人民法庭指示的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d7080bf82b"},{"id":"85a822ca8e","type":"paragraph","text":"客中央局，分局：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d7080bf82b"},{"id":"0b441c6711","type":"paragraph","text":"华东局关于组织人民法庭的指示“是正确的，望你们亦就需要情形发这样一个指示","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d7080bf82b"},{"id":"c54e92f683","type":"paragraph","text":"中央","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d7080bf82b"},{"id":"becbac9407","type":"paragraph","text":"八月十九日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d7080bf82b"}],"page":{"id":"15537fde33","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"d7080bf82b","start":90,"end":90}}}},"__N_SSG":true}